As a Host I can:
  1. Create an event
  2. Set a time
  3. Set a category
  4. Set a cost
  5. Set a location
  6. Determine number of guests that are allowed to attend
  7. Set attire
  8. Write a food bio

As an attendee I can
  1. Choose an event to attend
  2. I must pay the host's entrance fee
  3. Filter events
  